    {
        "content": "<p>Sorry, I don't know how to do a <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mwe.html\">#mwe</a>. Tried to copy and paste from <a href=\"http://live.lean-lang.org\">live.lean-lang.org</a> but unsuccessful.<br>\nexample {x y : \\Q} (h : (x - 1) * (y + 2) = 0) : x = 1 \\or y = -2</p>",
